flowRoot.flowPara: According to the Oromoo Gadaa system, every gadaa party holds power for eight (8) years and there are five(5) parties among which power rotates regularly. One complete rotation through each of the parties spans fourty(40) years, accordingly a person who lives 80 years will be able to see two (2) complete rotations a power - a power transition of 10 times.

I was inspired by the News about Mr Dhaqqaboo, from Arsii Lixaa, Washarbii who claimed to live 160 years old. He explains on VOA Afaan Oromoo "Dheerina Umurii Koo kana ani beeku Gadaa Shanan Marsa Afuur waanan argeef" which translates, I know (am sure of) my age because I have seen four complete rotation of gadaa parties among all gadaa parties.
According to a persons age-grade, one spans 40 years in the first
half of the cycle and another 40 in the second half.
